I'm so thankful, Father,

00:22:07.080 --> 00:22:09.350
that You are coming back and we'll be

00:22:09.360 --> 00:22:12.070
reunited with all our loved ones.

00:22:12.080 --> 00:22:13.030
It's

00:22:13.040 --> 00:22:16.070
just a glorious day. Oh, what a day of

00:22:16.080 --> 00:22:18.430
rejoicing that will be

00:22:18.440 --> 00:22:22.510
when we all get to heaven. We'll sing

00:22:22.520 --> 00:22:25.630
and shout the victory.

00:22:25.640 --> 00:22:29.310
Isn't that

00:22:29.320 --> 00:22:30.790
wonderful?

00:22:30.800 --> 00:22:32.910
It's going to be exciting.

00:22:34.840 --> 00:22:36.590
Everything we've ever believed for

00:22:39.560 --> 00:22:43.470
will be complete within

00:22:43.480 --> 00:22:45.430
our glorified

00:22:45.440 --> 00:22:47.270
bodies.

00:22:47.280 --> 00:22:50.230
We'll be standing before our King.

00:22:50.240 --> 00:22:53.230
Jesus Christ is coming;

00:22:53.240 --> 00:22:55.350
I just look forward to it.

00:22:57.960 --> 00:22:59.870
We take this body

00:22:59.870 --> 00:22:59.880
and

00:22:59.880 --> 00:23:01.390
thank You, Lord,

00:23:01.400 --> 00:23:03.190
for this time when everyone is

00:23:03.200 --> 00:23:04.950
focused on love. They

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:06.910
say we focus on Cupid

00:23:06.920 --> 00:23:08.670
and all that stuff, but no,

00:23:08.680 --> 00:23:10.710
I just love my wife.

00:23:10.720 --> 00:23:13.190
We have an extra day of just

00:23:13.200 --> 00:23:14.950
loving each

00:23:14.950 --> 00:23:14.960
other—an

00:23:14.960 --> 00:23:17.230
extra day of

00:23:17.240 --> 00:23:20.630
being on a honeymoon.

00:23:20.640 --> 00:23:23.430
I think it's a good time

00:23:23.440 --> 00:23:25.270
to reflect and rekindle

00:23:25.270 --> 00:23:25.280
the

00:23:25.280 --> 00:23:27.990
fire in your marriage.

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:29.830
You don't have to believe in all the

00:23:29.840 --> 00:23:31.630
weirdness.

00:23:31.640 --> 00:23:33.230
We just love each other, and it's a

00:23:33.240 --> 00:23:35.750
good day to love on your wife.

00:23:35.760 --> 00:23:37.150
Any day is a good day to love on your

00:23:37.160 --> 00:23:40.270
wife, but especially on Valentine's Day,

00:23:40.280 --> 00:23:42.870
try to be

00:23:44.640 --> 00:23:47.030
extra special.

00:23:48.160 --> 00:23:50.430
I think it's always

00:23:50.440 --> 00:23:51.830
good to

00:23:51.840 --> 00:23:54.230
sow love into the

00:23:54.240 --> 00:23:57.710
marriage and into the person who

00:23:57.710 --> 00:23:57.720
has given

00:23:57.720 --> 00:23:59.430
their

00:23:59.440 --> 00:24:02.070
life to you and given you children.

00:24:04.120 --> 00:24:05.390
Does that make sense?

00:24:06.000 --> 00:24:08.510
It's important. I think men don't need

00:24:08.520 --> 00:24:11.870
to be a fuddy-duddy. Be fun. Have fun.

00:24:11.880 --> 00:24:14.230
Be

00:24:14.230 --> 00:24:14.240
spontaneous.

00:24:14.240 --> 00:24:17.790
Love your spouse. Love your

00:24:17.790 --> 00:24:17.800
wives.

00:24:17.800 --> 00:24:19.630
Love your husbands. Pray with each

00:24:19.640 --> 00:24:20.830
other

00:24:20.830 --> 00:24:20.840
and

00:24:20.840 --> 00:24:22.510
honor each other.

00:24:22.520 --> 00:24:24.310
I really truly believe I can always

00:24:24.320 --> 00:24:26.110
feel when there's a flow

00:24:26.120 --> 00:24:27.670
in the spirit. I always say, "Okay,

00:24:27.680 --> 00:24:28.710
Diana,

00:24:28.710 --> 00:24:28.720
we've

00:24:28.720 --> 00:24:30.030
got to pray more together. We've got to

00:24:30.040 --> 00:24:31.190
read more together."You can feel it

00:24:31.200 --> 00:24:33.790
when you're in a covenant

00:24:33.800 --> 00:24:35.190
relationship and you're pushing

00:24:35.200 --> 00:24:37.750
together. For where two or three are

00:24:37.760 --> 00:24:39.710
gathered together in my name, there I am

00:24:39.720 --> 00:24:42.310
in the midst of them—Matthew 18:20.

00:24:56.840 --> 00:24:58.670
All glory to God.

00:24:58.680 --> 00:25:00.110
I believe that's what happens

00:25:00.120 --> 00:25:01.510
when you pray with your

00:25:01.510 --> 00:25:01.520
spouse.

00:25:01.520 --> 00:25:03.030
If

00:25:03.040 --> 00:25:04.110
you say, "I don't have

00:25:04.110 --> 00:25:04.120
anybody,"well,

00:25:04.120 --> 00:25:06.670
we'll be your two.

00:25:06.670 --> 00:25:06.680
Diana

00:25:06.680 --> 00:25:08.030
and I will agree with you. If

00:25:08.030 --> 00:25:08.040
you're

00:25:08.040 --> 00:25:09.550
single,

00:25:09.560 --> 00:25:11.350
we'll

00:25:11.360 --> 00:25:12.190
agree with you.

00:25:12.200 --> 00:25:14.190
That's why we're

00:25:14.190 --> 00:25:14.200
here—praying

00:25:14.200 --> 00:25:16.230
with you to agree with

00:25:16.240 --> 00:25:17.430
you. If you're a single

00:25:17.440 --> 00:25:19.070
mother or a single father

00:25:19.070 --> 00:25:19.080
and

00:25:19.080 --> 00:25:20.590
don't have anybody to

00:25:20.600 --> 00:25:22.350
agree with,

00:25:22.350 --> 00:25:22.360
Diana

00:25:22.360 --> 00:25:24.150
and I

00:25:24.160 --> 00:25:25.590
will agree with you.

00:25:25.600 --> 00:25:27.590
We pray and touch and agree, saying,

00:25:27.590 --> 00:25:27.600
"Whatever

00:25:27.600 --> 00:25:29.670
things are bound on

00:25:29.680 --> 00:25:30.910
earth are bound in heaven.

00:25:30.910 --> 00:25:30.920
Whatever

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:32.230
things are loosed on earth are loosed in

00:25:32.230 --> 00:25:32.240
heaven."We

00:25:32.240 --> 00:25:34.750
believe in the power of

00:25:34.760 --> 00:25:36.790
covenant

00:25:36.790 --> 00:25:36.800
and

00:25:36.800 --> 00:25:39.310
prayer. Whenever

00:25:39.320 --> 00:25:43.790
we agree, anything can be done.

00:25:43.800 --> 00:25:47.310
Two,

00:25:47.320 --> 00:25:48.910
three, four, or five

00:25:48.920 --> 00:25:50.630
agreeing—I

00:25:50.640 --> 00:25:53.430
believe with all my heart

00:25:53.430 --> 00:25:53.440
that

00:25:53.440 --> 00:25:55.590
many hands make light work.

00:25:55.600 --> 00:25:57.230
And so that's where we are in these end

00:25:57.230 --> 00:25:57.240
times—believing

00:25:57.240 --> 00:25:58.830
together as

00:25:58.840 --> 00:26:01.430
believers standing

00:26:01.430 --> 00:26:01.440
as

00:26:01.440 --> 00:26:03.190
a family. That's why we say

00:26:03.200 --> 00:26:05.390
"Good morning, family."We believe it.

00:26:05.400 --> 00:26:07.510
We are the body of Christ.

00:26:07.520 --> 00:26:10.550
People say, "I'm Catholic."I love the

00:26:10.560 --> 00:26:12.230
Catholics. Come on

00:26:12.240 --> 00:26:14.630
over here. We love the Church of Christ.

00:26:14.640 --> 00:26:17.150
We want the Baptists. We're

00:26:17.160 --> 00:26:19.190
not just about being charismatic

00:26:19.200 --> 00:26:21.270
here; we want the body of

00:26:21.280 --> 00:26:22.670
Christ. Now, you say, "Brandon,

00:26:22.680 --> 00:26:24.150
you say certain things."Well,

00:26:24.150 --> 00:26:24.160
yes,

00:26:24.160 --> 00:26:25.670
because I believe certain

00:26:25.680 --> 00:26:26.830
things, but I'm just saying that out of

00:26:26.840 --> 00:26:27.670
love.

00:26:29.960 --> 00:26:31.710
We can agree to disagree.

00:26:31.720 --> 00:26:33.510
I don't always agree with

00:26:33.520 --> 00:26:36.470
my extended family. You

00:26:36.480 --> 00:26:37.670
don't have to agree with everybody.

00:26:37.680 --> 00:26:40.270
I have aunts that believe

00:26:40.280 --> 00:26:42.310
in the whole

00:26:42.320 --> 00:26:44.030
tribulation and things like that, and

00:26:45.080 --> 00:26:47.190
I agree to disagree, but I

00:26:47.200 --> 00:26:49.270
still love

00:26:49.270 --> 00:26:49.280
them.

00:26:49.280 --> 00:26:51.390
It's amazing

00:26:51.400 --> 00:26:53.630
when you can just love each other

00:26:53.640 --> 00:26:56.070
in spite of differences.

00:26:56.080 --> 00:26:59.230
We don't have to be mean. You don't have

00:26:59.240 --> 00:27:00.870
to be a "Sister Clipboard"and pick on

00:27:00.880 --> 00:27:03.070
people. Just say, "Hey, we love you. We

00:27:03.080 --> 00:27:04.510
don't have to agree on

00:27:04.520 --> 00:27:06.590
everything. You're

00:27:06.600 --> 00:27:08.950
entitled to your

00:27:08.950 --> 00:27:08.960
opinion."We

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:10.150
still love you.

00:27:10.150 --> 00:27:10.160
On

00:27:10.160 --> 00:27:11.710
this day, we can focus

00:27:11.720 --> 00:27:14.910
on love. Love takes no account of a

00:27:14.920 --> 00:27:17.230
suffered wrong as we get ready

00:27:17.230 --> 00:27:17.240
for

00:27:17.240 --> 00:27:20.510
the day of love.

00:27:23.160 --> 00:27:26.390
God is love. Walk

00:27:26.400 --> 00:27:29.550
in love in the days ahead

00:27:29.560 --> 00:27:32.510
because

00:27:32.520 --> 00:27:35.150
faith works by love.

00:27:35.160 --> 00:27:37.030
If

00:27:37.040 --> 00:27:39.150
you feel like your faith is

00:27:39.160 --> 00:27:41.310
stagnant, check your love walk. I don't

00:27:41.320 --> 00:27:43.710
always agree with what people say and

00:27:43.720 --> 00:27:45.670
preach from the pulpit. But

00:27:45.680 --> 00:27:47.870
as

00:27:47.880 --> 00:27:49.910
Brother Hagin used to say

00:27:49.920 --> 00:27:51.710
all the time, you have to eat the hay and spit out the sticks. There's something good you

00:27:51.720 --> 00:27:53.710
can find in anything,

00:27:53.720 --> 00:27:55.070
but you have to eat the hay and spit out

00:27:55.080 --> 00:27:58.550
the sticks. And so that's what we do.

00:27:58.560 --> 00:28:01.550
Find books that help you grow.

00:28:01.560 --> 00:28:03.550
So Father, we thank you.

00:28:06.760 --> 00:28:08.350
I thank you, Father, for the body,

00:28:08.360 --> 00:28:09.950
and we take it right now. We believe

00:28:09.960 --> 00:28:12.990
that we receive your healing power

00:28:13.000 --> 00:28:14.950
that flows on the inside of us in the

00:28:14.960 --> 00:28:16.950
name of Jesus.

00:28:16.960 --> 00:28:20.310
We take the blood. We apply the blood,

00:28:20.320 --> 00:28:22.830
and the blood makes much of us.

00:28:22.840 --> 00:28:24.870
We plead the blood over

00:28:24.880 --> 00:28:26.870
our homes and over

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:29.270
our finances.

00:28:29.280 --> 00:28:31.230
We call those things that be not as

00:28:31.240 --> 00:28:34.790
though they were. We speak blessing,

00:28:34.800 --> 00:28:38.230
increase, multiplication, and favor

00:28:38.240 --> 00:28:41.630
over everything we put our hands to.

00:28:41.640 --> 00:28:43.990
We thank you, Lord, for what a God we

00:28:44.000 --> 00:28:46.550
serve, that we're blessed. We have

00:28:46.560 --> 00:28:50.070
increase, we have favor. We call

00:28:50.080 --> 00:28:51.350
in

00:28:51.360 --> 00:28:53.710
the

00:28:53.720 --> 00:28:55.710
financial seeds we sow; we call for a

00:28:55.720 --> 00:28:59.070
harvest over them: thirty, sixty,

00:28:59.070 --> 00:28:59.080
and a hundredfold.

00:28:59.080 --> 00:29:02.310
I speak to the seeds that I have sowed.

00:29:02.320 --> 00:29:05.870
You don't go dormant anymore; you spring

00:29:05.880 --> 00:29:09.870
forth much fruit in the name of Jesus.

00:29:09.880 --> 00:29:11.990
Now, angels of the Lord—we thank you,

00:29:11.990 --> 00:29:12.000
Lord—go,

00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:14.390
ministering spirits, and cause

00:29:14.400 --> 00:29:16.350
it to come forth

00:29:16.360 --> 00:29:19.030
in the name of Jesus. I call forth my

00:29:19.040 --> 00:29:22.670
harvest, a bountiful, beautiful harvest

00:29:22.680 --> 00:29:25.270
full of financial blessing.

00:29:25.280 --> 00:29:26.910
Now God, I thank you, Lord, that where

00:29:26.920 --> 00:29:29.110
I've sowed bad seed and

00:29:29.120 --> 00:29:31.590
we need a crop failure, I call for crop

00:29:31.600 --> 00:29:32.990
failure in the name of Jesus. I

00:29:33.000 --> 00:29:35.950
repent over the bad seeds I've sowed.

00:29:35.960 --> 00:29:37.470
Thank you, Lord, they're washed in the

00:29:37.480 --> 00:29:39.590
blood. Father, we call for crop

00:29:39.600 --> 00:29:41.670
failure over those seeds. We thank

00:29:41.680 --> 00:29:43.630
you, Lord, that over the ones we sowed

00:29:43.640 --> 00:29:45.710
that were bad, we call for crop

00:29:45.720 --> 00:29:47.870
failure. We say your blessing and grace

00:29:47.880 --> 00:29:50.350
covers it in the name of Jesus. And we

00:29:50.360 --> 00:29:53.910
thank you, Lord, that your hand is on

00:29:53.920 --> 00:29:55.830
those

00:29:55.840 --> 00:29:57.990
good seeds. The bad seeds

00:29:57.990 --> 00:29:58.000
are

00:29:58.000 --> 00:30:00.110
drying up and going away; the birds are

00:30:00.120 --> 00:30:02.230
eating them because we don't want to reap

00:30:02.240 --> 00:30:04.790
bad stuff. Seedtime and harvest never

00:30:04.790 --> 00:30:04.800
cease.

00:30:04.800 --> 00:30:07.470
Whatsoever a man sows, that will

00:30:07.470 --> 00:30:07.480
he

00:30:07.480 --> 00:30:09.550
also eat. You have good seed and you

00:30:09.550 --> 00:30:09.560
have

00:30:09.560 --> 00:30:11.350
bad seed. That's what I'm talking

00:30:11.360 --> 00:30:13.350
about.

00:30:13.360 --> 00:30:14.590
You think, 'Well, everything is good in

00:30:14.590 --> 00:30:14.600
mine.'Baloney.

00:30:15.630 --> 00:30:15.640
There

00:30:15.640 --> 00:30:18.110
are

00:30:18.120 --> 00:30:19.870
times when you

00:30:19.880 --> 00:30:21.670
might have sowed some bad seeds. You

00:30:21.680 --> 00:30:23.630
might have treated somebody badly or

00:30:23.630 --> 00:30:23.640
spoken to

00:30:23.640 --> 00:30:25.710
someone badly.

00:30:25.710 --> 00:30:25.720
There are

00:30:25.720 --> 00:30:28.110
bad seeds. You might have done

00:30:28.120 --> 00:30:30.390
something wrong,

00:30:30.400 --> 00:30:32.910
treated somebody disrespectfully, or

00:30:32.910 --> 00:30:32.920
done

00:30:32.920 --> 00:30:34.750
them wrong in business.

00:30:34.760 --> 00:30:36.430
I don't want to reap that. Father, we ask

00:30:36.440 --> 00:30:39.310
for repentance over these things. I thank you,

00:30:39.310 --> 00:30:39.320
Lord, for the blood.

00:30:39.320 --> 00:30:40.430
That's

00:30:41.680 --> 00:30:44.510
why

00:30:45.760 --> 00:30:47.590
we plead the

00:30:47.600 --> 00:30:49.390
blood and we make much of the blood, and

00:30:49.400 --> 00:30:52.230
the blood makes much of us. We apply the

00:30:52.240 --> 00:30:55.510
blood of Jesus over us in the name of

00:30:55.520 --> 00:30:58.190
Jesus. And we thank you, Lord. We thank

00:30:58.200 --> 00:31:00.110
you for the weather, the rain, and the harvest. We thank you, Lord,

00:31:03.760 --> 00:31:05.830
for the grass growing,

00:31:05.840 --> 00:31:07.790
the trees,

00:31:07.800 --> 00:31:09.950
and all the birds and beautiful

00:31:09.960 --> 00:31:11.550
things that you're providing for us.

00:31:11.560 --> 00:31:13.630
It's almost springtime, and we're so

00:31:13.640 --> 00:31:15.230
grateful, Father, that the weather

00:31:15.230 --> 00:31:15.240
is

00:31:15.240 --> 00:31:17.350
turning even prettier right now.

00:31:17.360 --> 00:31:19.190
God, we give you praise and glory for it

00:31:19.200 --> 00:31:21.390
right now in Jesus'name. We take

00:31:21.400 --> 00:31:23.350
this blood and apply

00:31:23.350 --> 00:31:23.360
it

00:31:23.360 --> 00:31:29.110
over us in Jesus'name. Amen and amen.

00:31:29.120 --> 00:31:32.430
Lord, we thank you for it.

00:31:32.440 --> 00:31:34.710
Father, I thank you. Right now, I

00:31:34.720 --> 00:31:36.790
plead the blood of Jesus over anything

00:31:36.800 --> 00:31:37.910
you want to show us. So

00:31:37.910 --> 00:31:37.920
that

00:31:37.920 --> 00:31:39.310
it

00:31:39.310 --> 00:31:39.320
is

00:31:39.320 --> 00:31:41.430
uninterrupted and unhindered by any

00:31:41.440 --> 00:31:45.510
satanic or demonic spirit, I apply the

00:31:45.520 --> 00:31:50.230
blood of Jesus over our prayer time.

00:31:50.240 --> 00:31:52.430
We thank you, Father, that the

00:31:52.440 --> 00:31:55.150
angels of the Lord are camping around and

00:31:55.160 --> 00:31:56.590
about us.

00:31:56.600 --> 00:31:59.070
Father, I plead the blood of Jesus

00:31:59.080 --> 00:32:02.470
over us, and we are not snared by

00:32:02.480 --> 00:32:04.870
any familiar spirits because we're

00:32:04.880 --> 00:32:09.110
always staying close to the Vine.

00:32:09.120 --> 00:32:11.710
Thank you, Father.

00:32:11.720 --> 00:32:13.830
We're so grateful

00:32:13.840 --> 00:32:16.470
for all that you've done and

00:32:16.480 --> 00:32:18.390
continue to do.

00:32:18.400 --> 00:32:20.310
We yield to the anointing

00:32:20.310 --> 00:32:20.320
of the prophet. I

00:32:20.320 --> 00:32:22.190
yield.

00:32:23.880 --> 00:32:26.150
Whatever you want to show

00:32:26.160 --> 00:32:29.390
me, Father, to warn the people,

00:32:29.400 --> 00:32:32.750
we humble ourselves before you.

00:32:32.760 --> 00:32:36.430
We attract to deflect.

00:32:36.440 --> 00:32:41.470
We don't use you;

00:32:41.480 --> 00:32:43.310
you use us.

00:32:43.320 --> 00:32:45.670
It's not about us trying to use you,

00:32:45.680 --> 00:32:47.710
Father. We're a vessel. You're the

00:32:47.720 --> 00:32:50.150
potter; we're the clay.

00:32:51.600 --> 00:32:54.590
We humble ourselves before you today.

00:32:54.600 --> 00:32:57.710
We know that apart from you, we can do

00:32:57.720 --> 00:32:59.550
nothing.

00:33:02.520 --> 00:33:12.270
As He is, so are we in this world.

00:33:12.280 --> 00:33:16.190
I thank you, Father.

00:33:16.200 --> 00:33:20.910
What can wash away my sin?

00:33:20.920 --> 00:33:26.790
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:33:26.800 --> 00:33:31.590
What can make me whole again?

00:33:31.600 --> 00:33:34.793
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:33:37.280 --> 00:33:40.630
Oh, precious

00:33:40.640 --> 00:33:43.470
is the flow

00:33:43.480 --> 00:33:50.390
that makes me white as snow.

00:33:50.400 --> 00:33:52.790
No

00:33:52.800 --> 00:33:55.390
other

00:33:55.390 --> 00:33:55.400
fount

00:33:55.400 --> 00:33:56.910
I know,

